  <p>Keeps tape cartridges clean for   long life and better performance.</span> Regular cleaning of the drive reduces build-up or stains that have been deposited on the head.</p>
  <p>The cleaning process is unique to each drive format. Generally, there are dry cleaning and wet cleaning methods. Use the correct cleaning method for your network system protocol and ensure data integrity. </p>
  
  
